<i>Yeah,
I took up painting</i>

02:23.578 --> 02:25.232
during season two
of <i>Grounded for Life.</i>

02:25.275 --> 02:26.711
As an actor,
you spend a lot of time

02:26.755 --> 02:28.452
sitting around your trailer,
waiting for them

02:28.496 --> 02:30.193
to light the next scene
or whatnot,

02:30.237 --> 02:33.327
so I got some brushes
and a how-to book from Blick,

02:33.370 --> 02:34.893
and I think I've gotten
pretty good.

02:34.937 --> 02:37.244
<i>This is the cast of
Grounded for Life.</i>

02:37.287 --> 02:39.550
<i>Oh, my God, Jake and Griffin
were so squirrely,</i>

02:39.594 --> 02:41.378
<i>I was like,
"Look, here's the deal.</i>

02:41.422 --> 02:43.598
"I'm gonna take a picture,
and then you guys can fuck off

02:43.641 --> 02:45.991
