from a photo, but you know,</i>

02:48.646 --> 02:50.866
that's the way a lot
of the masters work now.

02:50.909 --> 02:53.477
<i>This is the front gate
of Radford in Studio City.</i>

02:53.521 --> 02:55.653
<i>I was really happy with
the way the light reflected</i>

02:55.697 --> 02:57.525
<i>off the admin building
that day.</i>

02:57.568 --> 03:00.049
